Description: Funds increased test requirements, such as targets, range and instrumentation costs, and Other Government
Agency (OGA) test and evaluation support for capability set fielding and continuous transformation efforts.

FY 2027 Plans:
FY 2027 funding will enable competition and evaluation of emerging technologies, such as Low Collateral Defeat (LCD) and
alternate sensing solutions, to inform capability set fielding. Funding will support acquisition of additional test and evaluation legal

