Description: The Manufacturing Enterprise/Other activity includes: (1) efforts targeted towards improving,
in general, the manufacturing enterprise for the production of key naval platforms (both shipbuilding and
aircraft); (2) energetics efforts; (3) naval research enterprise and laboratory support for key projects; and (4)
