streamlining of outfitting operations; prediction and reduction of welding distortion; advanced automation and
robotics for manufacturing; advanced data analytics, artificial intelligence and machine learning for production
environments; and inspection technologies such as digital radiography and ultrasonic technologies. Energetics
efforts concentrate on developing energetics solutions to ensure the availability of safe, affordable, and quality
energetics products largely in support of Program Executive Office (PEO) Integrated Warfare Systems (IWS).

